version 3.1
  * Initial RPM release.
  * The following development changes where added since the last release (0.9)
    * Improved database robustness
    * Support for query and update messages that look more like LS messages
    * Updated example topology and requests
  * Bugfixes
    - http://code.google.com/p/perfsonar-ps/issues/detail?id=149
      the TL1 status collector doesn't handle timeouts well   	 
    - http://code.google.com/p/perfsonar-ps/issues/detail?id=150
      Status service might erroneously list status as "unknown" 
